{"tid":284768,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[學是學非]《明報》知多啲﹕鴉片、嗎啡、白粉本是同根生","createTime":"2017-06-15T08:14:22.000Z","updateTime":"2017-06-18T11:06:28.000Z","uid":79563,"like":13,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"2c989aeddf948be4eb2c3fed55483627c15284dd","tid":284768,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-15T08:14:22.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://news.mingpao.com/pns/知多啲﹕鴉片嗎啡白粉本是同根生/web_tc/article/20141027/s00005/1414347140416\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fpns%2F%E7%9F%A5%E5%A4%9A%E5%95%B2%EF%B9%95%E9%B4%89%E7%89%87%E5%97%8E%E5%95%A1%E7%99%BD%E7%B2%89%E6%9C%AC%E6%98%AF%E5%90%8C%E6%A0%B9%E7%94%9F%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20141027%2Fs00005%2F1414347140416&d=lxsB7AtX3krfHzn%2BLtkFW1eK4D04he4k8uKHxpzC8zE%3D&h=38caf1f1\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fpns%2F%E7%9F%A5%E5%A4%9A%E5%95%B2%EF%B9%95%E9%B4%89%E7%89%87%E5%97%8E%E5%95%A1%E7%99%BD%E7%B2%89%E6%9C%AC%E6%98%AF%E5%90%8C%E6%A0%B9%E7%94%9F%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20141027%2Fs00005%2F1414347140416&h=28f04133\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.mingpao.com/pns/知多啲﹕鴉片嗎啡白粉本是同根生/web_tc/article/20141027/s00005/1414347140416</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://fs.mingpao.com/pns/20141027/s00117/1414410574573_72F3458C73B56AA2932B853B87E76053.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffs.mingpao.com%2Fpns%2F20141027%2Fs00117%2F1414410574573_72F3458C73B56AA2932B853B87E76053.jpg&h=c2198b88&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n圖2之1 - 由罌粟（上圖）提煉而成的鴉片，進一步提煉成嗎啡，再加工則是海洛英（下圖）。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://fs.mingpao.com/pns/20141027/s00117/1414410575010_A887EBEB65B9C810CCBA1649A81B601D.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffs.mingpao.com%2Fpns%2F20141027%2Fs00117%2F1414410575010_A887EBEB65B9C810CCBA1649A81B601D.jpg&h=3420ac06&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n【明報專訊】晚清時期，抽鴉片成風。不少人每天在鴉片中醉生夢死，最終體力受損、精神萎靡，成為了東亞病夫。精神科專科醫生張偉謙指出，從罌粟提煉而成的鴉片，原來進一步提煉就是嗎啡；嗎啡再進一步加工，則是俗稱白粉的海洛英。<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: orange;\">嗎啡需處方 亂用可致死</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n和大麻相近，嗎啡也具有鎮痛作用。「嗎啡具有醫學用途，主要的用途是止痛，常應用於末期癌症或嚴重痛症。當一般常用止痛藥未能止痛，會考慮處方藥效強烈的嗎啡。」張偉謙解釋，嗎啡能刺激大腦的受體，減低對痛的知覺。「效果和吸白粉相近，也會令人感到輕鬆舒暢，所以嗎啡需經醫生處方，以免濫用。」<br />\n<br />\n張醫生指出，嗎啡的副作用包括嘔吐、手震、昏昏欲睡、記憶力衰退，「除此之外，嗎啡會壓抑腦幹呼吸中樞，令人呼吸困難。使用不當會暈眩，甚或缺氧而死，分量必須控制得當。至於海洛英，雖然也有鎮痛作用，卻較嗎啡更易上癮、後遺症更深，所以不會應用在醫學上」。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">文﹕陳雅君</span></span>"},{"pid":"8959fe7a7ea3605e731ee923101295e4b57e2c73","tid":284768,"uid":22858,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-15T08:18:52.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/15.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/15.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/15.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9e62b2911fac56fcf17e3064f375ccf9602018cb","tid":284768,"uid":122233,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-15T08:38:36.000Z","msg":"陳雅君準備收信"},{"pid":"125d0fedfca92c440f3b4334fdc0938f9e260d50","tid":284768,"uid":31354,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-15T08:39:38.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong>陳雅君</strong></span></span>好撚橙<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0999165e2a3169a8c07ff8fba463d144034f119b","tid":284768,"uid":16256,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-15T08:39:56.000Z","msg":"告埋明報"},{"pid":"28041bdc484dce53e5ddd59ca707b8dc33fa1b04","tid":284768,"uid":1654,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-15T09:04:49.000Z","msg":"雖難必誅！！"},{"pid":"0e38375d903df8a88808c69837a69bfc3f22753f","tid":284768,"uid":48796,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-15T09:06:26.000Z","msg":"要求明報道歉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f054a7aecd31deef5c8936b8d3a96c41d43d4bc5","tid":284768,"uid":110964,"l